<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA515_07_IH_0007_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema511_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema515_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_07_ih_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="7" class="is_star2" lang="y">수 카드 3장을 한 번씩만 사용하여 만들 수 있는 가장 큰 대분수와 가장 작은 대분수의 차를 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="left">
              <div class="img_box">
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA515_07_IH/0007_img.png" alt="" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
              <h3 class="title" lang="y">만들 수 있는 가장 큰 대분수와 가장 작은 대분수를<br />각각 구해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="flex justify_center">
                <div class="flex dir_col align_end gap_20">
                  <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
                    <span lang="y">가장 큰 대분수:</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="7" class="w_80"></math-field>
                      </div>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex align_center gap_12">
                    <span lang="y">가장 작은 대분수:</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
                      </div>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <!--start solve-->
                  <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                    만들 수 있는 가장 큰 대분수는&nbsp;
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>7</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>1</span>
                        <span>4</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    이고, 가장 작은 대분수는
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>4</span>
                        <span>7</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    입니다.
                  </div>
                  <!--end solve-->
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="left">
              <div class="img_box">
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA515_07_IH/0007_img.png" alt="" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
              <h3 class="title" lang="y">앞에서 구한 두 분수의 차를 구해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="flex justify_center">
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <div class="bracket">
                    <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="5" class="w_80"></math-field>
                      </div>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="19"></math-field>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                          <math-field data-answer-single="28"></math-field>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="bracket-r"></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <!--start solve-->
                  <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>7</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>1</span>
                        <span>4</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <span>-</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>4</span>
                        <span>7</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <span>=</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>7</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>7</span>
                        <span>28</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <span>-</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>16</span>
                        <span>28</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <span>=</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>6</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>35</span>
                        <span>28</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <span>-</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>16</span>
                        <span>28</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <span>=</span>
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>5</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>19</span>
                        <span>28</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <!--end solve-->
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
